Wizkid throws beach party Grammy award-winning Nigerian Singer, Wizkid was in his ‘chilling’ element when he threw a beach party in his Ghana mansion which attracted one of his close friends, Kim Oprah. The Nigerian superstar is a lover of parties that tend to serve as a break away from his busy schedules. Wizkid hosted the party shortly after he was spotted in a viral video stepping out with a ‘Ghana Must Go bag’ full of money. The ”Essence’ hit-maker also invited industry colleagues like Wande Coal, Phyno, Actress Osas Ighodaro and of course, the sexy looking ladies to the star-studded event. They were all in a cozy mood vibing to Wande Coal’s smash hit single ‘Come my way’. See video below: [embedded content]